{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5919", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5919/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5919/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5919/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/datalad/datalad/issues/5919", "id": 974678971, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU5NzQ2Nzg5NzE=", "number": 5919, "title": "Hint the user if lots of content was committed directly to git", "user": {"login": "yarikoptic", "id": 39889, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM5ODg5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/39889?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic", "html_url": "https://github.com/yarikoptic", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yarikoptic/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 390153891, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwzOTAxNTM4OTE=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/labels/UX", "name": "UX", "color": "0052cc", "default": false, "description": "user experience"}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2021-08-19T13:43:13Z", "updated_at": "2021-08-19T15:43:36Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "#### What is the problem?\r\n\r\nuse cases: many in my own history, and a recent one https://neurostars.org/t/datalad-dataset-cleaning-questions/20052/9 \r\n\r\nIf at the end of save we could assess how much content was committed directly into git, and if it is notable (e.g. committed > 100MB or (.git/objects became > 100MB and commit increased it by over 100%)) -- inform the user\r\n\r\n- if it is a pure git repo -- inform to use git-annex\r\n- if it is an annexed repo -- inform the user to adjust .gitattributes to fit their case better\r\n\r\nalong side -- provide some extra guidance e.g. show largest file committed; point to ways to mitigate (somewhere in handbook?)\r\n\r\nI guess it should be able to turn off such hints globally off via config", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5919/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5919/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}